    <briefdescription>
<para>Called when a block explodes (e.g. bed in the Nether, respawn anchor in the Overworld). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>If a <ref refid="classendstone_1_1BlockExplodeEvent" kindref="compound">BlockExplodeEvent</ref> is cancelled, the explosion will not occur. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
